OL,7,FA decision has been made not to
OL,8,Fintroduce birthing facilities the
OL,9,FGalloway Community Hospital, leaving
OL,10,Fpregnant women with a long diversion
OL,11,Fto get to the nearest facility.
OL,13,FThe Dumfries and Galloway Integration
OL,14,FJoint Board made the decision
OL,15,Ffollowing an independently-led review
OL,16,Fand public consultation.
OL,18,FThe home birthing model will be
OL,19,Fretained "for the foreseeable future."
