OL,7,FChairman of the IJB (Integration Joint
OL,8,FBoard) Andy McFarlane said: "One thing
OL,9,FI would want to stress from the start
OL,10,Fis our confidence as a Board in the
OL,11,Fmaternity services as they stand
OL,12,Fcurrently across the region, including
OL,13,FWigtownshire.
OL,15,F"It was acknowledged that care is of a
OL,16,Fvery high standard, and it was noted
OL,17,Fthat there is an enhanced offer
OL,18,Fdelivered through the Oak Tree Family
OL,19,FCentre."
