OL,7,FThe decision to retain the current
OL,8,Fmodel he says was "not an easy one"
OL,9,Fand that it is due to "staff
OL,10,Fshortages."
OL,12,FHe said: "The decision about provision
OL,13,Fof birthing services in Wigtownshire
OL,14,Fwas not an easy one to arrive at, as
OL,15,Fevery member of the board is acutely
OL,16,Faware of calls from communities to
OL,17,Fhave the fullest range of services
OL,18,Fmade available locally.
