OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"We were fully informed, thanks to the
OL,8,Freview and the consultation, of the
OL,9,Fissues faced by expectant mothers in
OL,10,Fterms of travelling to give birth in
OL,11,FDumfries.
OL,13,F"This is a situation which dates from
OL,14,F2018, when birthing services within
OL,15,FGalloway Community Hospital were
OL,16,Fsuspended on a temporary basis due to
OL,17,Funexpected staff shortages."
OL,19,FAndy explained how the current model
OL,20,Fis the best one they could have in
OL,21,Fplace.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
