OL,7,FHe said: "Taking on board the original
OL,8,Freport, all of the facts, and all of
OL,9,Fthe thoughts and perspectives, the IJB
OL,10,Fconcluded that the status quo
OL,11,Frepresents the best and most
OL,12,Fdeliverable and sustainable model now
OL,13,Fand for the foreseeable future.
