OL,4,Cas return to maternity services ruled
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"Introducing this service at Galloway
OL,8,FCommunity Hospital for what would be a
OL,9,Fsmall number of eligible expectant
OL,10,Fmothers would not represent a
OL,11,Fsignificant difference from a home
OL,12,Fbirth, as the resources in terms of
OL,13,Fmidwifery staff who would be on hand
OL,14,Fto provide support would be exactly
OL,15,Fthe same. Only the setting would
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
