OL,3,C70 mile journey to give birth remains
OL,4,Cas return to maternity services ruled
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"And while we would ideally want to
OL,8,Foffer an option of a hospital birth
OL,9,Fwhich does not require travelling to
OL,10,FDumfries, we recognised that neither
OL,11,Fapproach would actually end this
OL,12,Frequirement for the majority of
OL,13,Fexpectant mothers.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
