OL,3,C70 mile journey to give birth remains
OL,4,Cas return to maternity services ruled
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"We also considered what was
OL,8,Fdeliverable safely at present, and the
OL,9,Ffact that both across the region and
OL,10,Fnationally there is a routine
OL,11,Frequirement on mothers to make
OL,12,Fsometimes quite lengthy journeys to
OL,13,Flocations where birthing services can
OL,14,Fbe provided.
OL,16,F"This has been a challenging decision
OL,17,Fon what is a very personal and
OL,18,Femotional subject, where there is
OL,19,Fgreat strength of feeling, and where
OL,20,Fwe as a Board recognise a commitment
OL,21,Fto patient-centred care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
