OL,4,Cas return to maternity services ruled
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"In conclusion, the Board agreed that
OL,8,Fthe approach which serves the majority
OL,9,Fof expectant mothers in Wigtownshire
OL,10,Fis the one which is reasonable and
OL,11,Fappropriate for all, but with that
OL,12,Fcontinuing option of home birth."
